name: Still Life 16.2
description:
Fizz Pop (b.1974)  
September 2021  
7500 x 6000 pixels  

  This sheaf of wheat consists of 20 stalks, representing the 20 Still Life paintings minted on Hic et Nunc at the beginning of September.  As a gesture of appreciation, the 87 collectors who hold a Still Life from this collection, receive an edition of this work in their wallet.
